[SN]TITLE[SN]
Teenagers found hiding under cannabis farm floorboards

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Two teenagers were found hiding under the floorboards of a cannabis farm during a police raid.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The pair, aged 18 and 17, were discovered during the search, which also uncovered about 100 marijuana plants inside the house in Liverpool.
